              "answer": "(a) At top, v = 0. t = u/g = 25/9.8 = 2.55 s. (b) h = u²/(2g) = 625/19.6 = 31.9 m. (c) By symmetry, t_total = 2 × 2.55 = 5.10 s. Or solve s = 0: 0 = 25t − 4.9t² → t = 0 or t = 25/4.9 = 5.10 s."
