          { "question": "Light enters water (n = 1.33) from air at 30°. Find the angle of refraction.", "answer": "n₁ sin θ₁ = n₂ sin θ₂: 1.0 × sin 30° = 1.33 × sin θ₂. sin θ₂ = 0.5/1.33 = 0.376. θ₂ = 22.1°. Bends toward normal (entering denser medium) ✓." }
